title: RHOC: The Weight Is Over!
description:
"The Real Housewives of Orange County" is back, and you guys, we really dug the season premiere. Is the slump over??? Time will tell. But for now, we're optimistic! Come join us as we discuss Single Shannon, Young Gravy, and Gina's "Antiques!" box.

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.

author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (Ben Mandelker & Ronnie Karam)
